info.author: Carl Vitzthum
classifiers: Topic :: Software Development :: Libraries :: Python Modules
info.name: hic2cool
info.summary: Converter between .hic files (from juicer) and .cool files (for cooler).  Both hic and cool files describe Hi-C contact matrices. Intended to be lightweight, this can be used as a simple imported package or a stand-alone Python file for command line conversion.
